!!****d* ABINIT/lib_bigdft
!! NAME
!! lib_bigdft
!!
!! DESCRIPTION
!! This subdirectory contains the BigDFT code which gives routines to handle
!! a wavelet basis for wave-functions.
!! These routines do not follow the ABINIT coding rules
!! (~abinit/doc/developers/rules_coding).
